Package: PopGenBounds
Type: Package
Title: Bounds on population-genetic statistics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Nicolas", "Alcala", email="alcalan@iarc.fr", role = c("aut", "cre"),comment=c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5961-5064"))
Maintainer: Nicolas Alcala <alcalan@iarc.fr>
Description: This package computes the range of possible values for
    various statistics from the population genetics literature. It considers
    different scenarios, and provides functions to plot data within these ranges.
